---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import { Code } from "astro:components";
import ContentSection from "~/components/content-section.astro";
---

<ContentSection title="Cue the Aladdin Soundtrack" id="intro">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    <span class="text-center">
      Marketing Just Entered <br /><span class="italic text-orange"
        >A Whole New World</span
      >
    </span>
  </Fragment>
  <div class="m-auto text-darksteel">
    <div class="flex flex-row gap-20 text-left">
      <div class="flex-1 md:w-2/3">
        <p>
          We’re living in unprecedented times: today the use of AI in business
          is rapidly expanding.
          <span class="font-bold">
            But when everyone else is turning to AI to grow their business, the
            way to stand out in this increasingly artificial world is to be
            relatably, authentically yourself.
          </span>
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class="font-bold text-orange">
          The competitive advantage you've been looking for is genuine
          human-to-human connection.
        </p>
        <br />
        <p>
          Marketing For Humans is the proven system for solopreneurs to <span
            class="font-bold"
            >learn how to grow your business, attract your ideal customers, and
            generate more revenue than you thought possible</span
          > — all through the power of marketing like a human.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center md:w-1/3">
        <img
          class="w-full max-w-96 rotate-3"
          src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/5f2ae813361eff3ad9282b29/63e69408eaf0942910cd57b8_B-School_iMac-p-800.png"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</ContentSection>
